Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:02.10,0:00:03.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,數據更新
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.81,0:00:06.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,軌道轉換完成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.94,0:00:09.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,監視器拜託了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.15,0:00:13.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,DS-12 這裡是7號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.48,0:00:12.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的腿還好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.22,0:00:14.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:17.22,0:00:18.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.45,0:00:19.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是看過好多次了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.06,0:00:21.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話雖如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.72,0:00:24.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次從宇宙看地球的時候飄飄然的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:25.16,0:00:27.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但經歷許多事後再看到地球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:28.20,0:00:29.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有新的感動嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.97,0:00:31.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:35.74,0:00:37.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,極光真漂亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.71,0:00:43.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前輩 我還想再回到這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:44.38,0:00:45.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為殘骸工
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:46.92,0:00:48.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能回來 一定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.09,0:00:52.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們在說什麼呀？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:53.42,0:00:54.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 課長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:54.62,0:00:55.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能偷聽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.82,0:00:59.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是作為上司有義務監督年輕人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.00,0:01:00.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,義務？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.96,0:01:02.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是義務就沒辦法了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.00,0:01:07.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You copy？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:07.87,0:01:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I copy
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.54,0:01:10.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣不好 課長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.31,0:01:12.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.61,0:01:16.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMS PGothic}け...ケスラーシンドローム
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.61,0:01:16.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}克斯拉症候群
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:16.48,0:01:19.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMS PGothic}む...無重量用軸受け
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:16.48,0:01:19.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}失重用時空儀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:19.38,0:01:20.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMS PGothic}ケネス
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:19.38,0:01:20.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}天體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:20.58,0:01:21.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMS PGothic}す？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.45,0:01:23.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMS PGothic}スピン抜け
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.45,0:01:23.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}回旋拉升
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:23.65,0:01:25.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMS PGothic}け...計器飛行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:23.65,0:01:25.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}儀器導航
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.29,0:01:27.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMS PGothic}ウインドウ開け
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.29,0:01:27.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}開視窗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:27.82,0:01:29.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMS PGothic}ケネディー宇宙センター、あ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:27.82,0:01:29.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}克雷迪宇宙中心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:30.16,0:01:30.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是{\fnMS PGothic}あ{\r}嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.39,0:01:33.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMS PGothic}アナンケ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.39,0:01:33.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}木星的第十二顆衛星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.56,0:01:37.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMS PGothic}鍵盤ハーモニカ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.56,0:01:37.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}鍵盤口琴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.43,0:01:38.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMS PGothic}髪の毛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.43,0:01:38.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}頭髮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.63,0:01:39.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是{\fnMS PGothic}け{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.64,0:01:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒詞了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.14,0:01:43.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMS PGothic}け...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.21,0:01:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.81,0:01:52.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMS PGothic}結婚しよう
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.81,0:01:52.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}結婚吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.82,0:01:54.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是{\fnMS PGothic}う{\r}了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.52,0:01:59.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMS PGothic}うん
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.52,0:01:59.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.39,0:02:01.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 你輸了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.39,0:02:01.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}先說到{\fnMS PGothic}ん{\r}{\fs20}算輸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.03,0:04:23.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是九太郎吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.03,0:04:26.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家裡有兩個人去了木星有何感受？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.50,0:04:28.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼話要對父親和哥哥說？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.40,0:04:29.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.14,0:04:31.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓開 讓開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.57,0:04:33.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這麼說嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.98,0:04:36.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請讓道 請讓道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.61,0:04:37.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵守規定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.15,0:04:42.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真辛苦呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.49,0:04:44.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.45,0:04:45.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回來啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.72,0:04:46.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像很熱鬧呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.32,0:04:49.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是拒絕採訪了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.26,0:04:50.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們在想什麼呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.99,0:04:53.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時候你還沒出生可能不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.96,0:04:56.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你父親去火星的時候也這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.17,0:05:02.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經開始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.57,0:05:04.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小愛 小愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.34,0:05:05.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經開始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.34,0:05:07.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.11,0:05:09.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些事我做就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.81,0:05:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這點事不要緊的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.61,0:05:13.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 你太在意了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.98,0:05:14.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煩死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.48,0:05:16.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過來坐這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.32,0:05:18.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽也快點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.85,0:05:19.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.19,0:05:22.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才最興奮呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.06,0:05:30.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}今天是人類智慧的結晶...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.23,0:05:30.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.30,0:05:34.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八郎太好緊張呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.77,0:05:38.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}這是什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.11,0:05:40.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}星野引擎長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.78,0:05:43.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}父親對飛行員兒子的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.81,0:05:47.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是國際直播呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.25,0:05:48.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真丟人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.75,0:05:49.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.68,0:05:50.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和平時一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.79,0:05:52.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這可是木星呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.65,0:05:53.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽也是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.92,0:05:54.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個晾完了就去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.99,0:05:56.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衣服什麼的明天也可以洗呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.46,0:05:58.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.66,0:06:02.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做這種人的老婆還真...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.20,0:06:05.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.27,0:06:08.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然說這種話有點晚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.57,0:06:09.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓他去真的好嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.97,0:06:12.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母親還好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.71,0:06:13.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小愛可是新婚呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.44,0:06:15.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.74,0:06:17.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要分開7年呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.45,0:06:19.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.68,0:06:20.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.78,0:06:23.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 萬一...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.75,0:06:26.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.46,0:06:28.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們約好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.86,0:06:30.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.20,0:06:34.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不明白


